   &lt;span style=&quot;font-family: calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: calibri;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;David C. Schwebel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;mso-ascii-font-family: calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin&quot;&gt;：教授，美国阿拉巴马大学心理学系科研副主任、青少年安全实验室主任，美国心理学协会会员，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: calibri;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;Woodrow Wilson&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;mso-ascii-font-family: calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin&quot;&gt;学者，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: calibri;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;Fulbright&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;mso-ascii-font-family: calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin&quot;&gt;奖获得者。主要研究方向是儿童、青少年及年轻成年人非故意伤害的认识和预防。主持&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: calibri;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;NIH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;mso-ascii-font-family: calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: calibri;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;CDC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;mso-ascii-font-family: calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: calibri;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;DOT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;mso-ascii-font-family: calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin&quot;&gt;等部门的项目，与其它联邦机构、非营利组织及行业组织密切合作，发表论文&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: calibri;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;160&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;mso-ascii-font-family: calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin&quot;&gt;余篇。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 19px&quot;&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
