&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 37px;mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;许茜，博士、教授，中国检验检疫学会理事、江苏省食品安全标准审评专家、江苏省预防医学会卫生检验专业委员会委员。现任东南大学公共卫生学院营养与食品卫生系副主任，主要研究方向为分析样品前处理新技术及其在食品安全分析和环境检测方面的应用、污染物膳食暴露致病风险评估。主持国家级和省部级科研项目&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;项，第一发明人已授权国家发明专利&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;项，发表第一作者或通讯作者科研论文近&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;60&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;篇，其中&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;SCI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;或&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;EI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &apos;times new roman&apos;;font-size: 19px;mso-spacerun: &apos;yes&apos;;mso-font-kerning: 1px&quot;&gt;收录论文&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-famil